{"tid":1419263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請睇睇朱凱廸 - 罷工的焦點應放到打工仔身上","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:57:11.000Z","uid":291996,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a09cfd9402bf5372a8f3f5277d3719bfe73384e","tid":1419263,"uid":291996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:38:17.000Z","msg":"Quote: 今日三罷，主角應該是罷工罷市的打工仔和商戶，以及強調罷工所產生的威力。可惜我們缺乏公關部署，結果傳媒很快以朝早的堵路和下午開始的衝擊蓋過罷工&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n由現在起到今晚，希望大家有意識地將焦點重新放到罷工的打工仔和公務員身上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八鄉朱凱廸 Chu Hoi Dick<br />\n<br />\nQuoted from 立埸新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%87%89%E6%94%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2584%25A6%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25B8%258A%2F&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=482c7ac8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2584%25A6%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25B8%258A%2F&h=f1e31021\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%87%89%E6%94%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣組可唔可以幫手？"},{"pid":"55f48944a29a3b9cf718770bf813195719b93a15","tid":1419263,"uid":291996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a0c7e22502a16a33cf1235da2315431b06732a3","tid":1419263,"uid":291996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:38:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25d1b2bf6c5fe1350